00:01:15.542 --> 00:01:20.079
NOW, WE CAN ALSO CATEGORIZE
OUR RECEPTORS

00:01:20.146 --> 00:01:23.782
BY THE KIND OF STIMULUS
THAT THEY PICK UP.

00:01:23.849 --> 00:01:25.051
SO LET'S MAKE A LIST

00:01:25.117 --> 00:01:28.754
OF ALL THE POSSIBLE TYPES
OF SENSORY RECEPTORS

