THAT WE CAN COME UP WITH,

00:01:30.489 --> 00:01:32.124
AND THEN WHAT I'M GOING
TO TELL YOU IS THAT

00:01:32.191 --> 00:01:34.760
WE'RE GOING TO GO THROUGH
